    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what difference does it even make though? like, i see these people talking about \"incremental change\" and it just feels like they're rearranging the deck chairs on the titanic. it's all just delaying the unavoidable. it feels more like we're just prolonging the suffering for no reason at all. it feels like the most honest response to everything is just to stop fighting it.",
